videos.title: Chain Veil Superfriends
videos.description:
Back when Pioneer first came out, there was a Fires of Invention superfriends deck. Its time to revisit it with Chain Veil, Jace, Architect of Thought, and Gideon, Ally of Zendikar on Arena now!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish

► Read more about this deck (full article): https://www.mtggoldfish.com/articles/single-scoop-chain-veil-superfriends
